Excellent course!

Rewarding and engaging topic and module to read and study on. Found the lectures concise, with varying layers of reading topics and material.  Gained such a deeper level of Cyber Security than I intended, bringing together various fields, I didn't have a firm grip or knowledge in. Sound style of delivery in the content and lectures. Did replay some to be certain I understood the content.  Read a lot of terminology, that I didn't have awareness of before and found some reading articles quite hard  to fully handle. I made such advances in how I see and now understand cyber security, networks and systems. Much, much more I wanted to learn and gain. Will be acquiring it to advance career IT knowledge in government departments or when I return abroad again. Made me really think !
